Tuesday, December 14, 1999

MERIT DOCKET

99-1977. Cotten v. Wilkinson.

In Prohibition. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of prohibition. *1467Upon consideration of respondents’ answer,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
